 There is air in it. 

00:01:01.220 --> 00:01:03.560
 The air consists mainly of nitrogen. 

00:01:03.560 --> 00:01:06.720
 To make it simple, let it be full of nitrogen only. 

00:01:06.780 --> 00:01:10.660
 I'll paint nitrogen molecules. 

00:01:10.660 --> 00:01:13.460
 We have a thermometer. 

00:01:13.460 --> 00:01:16.040
 I put him in court. 

