 the other, 

00:03:33.580 --> 00:03:35.132
 and this. 

00:03:35.132 --> 00:03:37.200
 If you compare this system with this, 

00:03:37.200 --> 00:03:40.440
 you will still find a separate molecule, 

00:03:40.440 --> 00:03:41.800
 which moves very fast. 

00:03:41.800 --> 00:03:43.060
 It can even move faster 

00:03:43.060 --> 00:03:44.800
 from any molecule in the first system. 

00:03:44.800 --> 00:03:46.840
 But the average kinetic energy 

00:03:46.840 --> 00:03:48.730
 of molecules here is lower. 

